### Activity Logs

# Get user activity
GET http://localhost:3000/activity?limit=50&offset=0

###

# Get recent activity
GET http://localhost:3000/activity/recent?limit=20

###

### Batch Operations

# Batch delete
POST http://localhost:3000/files/batch/delete
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "items": [
    { "id": "file-uuid-1", "type": "file" },
    { "id": "folder-uuid-1", "type": "folder" }
  ]
}

###

# Batch move
POST http://localhost:3000/files/batch/move
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "items": [
    { "id": "file-uuid-1", "type": "file" },
    { "id": "folder-uuid-1", "type": "folder" }
  ],
  "targetFolderId": "target-folder-uuid-or-null"
}

###

# Batch restore
POST http://localhost:3000/files/batch/restore
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "items": [
    { "id": "file-uuid-1", "type": "file" },
    { "id": "folder-uuid-1", "type": "folder" }
  ]
}

###

### File Preview & Thumbnails

# Get file thumbnail (for images)
GET http://localhost:3000/files/<file-id>/thumbnail

###

# Get file preview (inline viewing)
GET http://localhost:3000/files/<file-id>/preview

###

# Get file metadata
GET http://localhost:3000/files/<file-id>/metadata

###

### Folder Download

# Download folder as ZIP
GET http://localhost:3000/folders/<folder-id>/download
